OL,3,CMeet the train fanatic using his
OL,4,Ctracks to help local causes
OL,6,FDespite this, Curtis says there is
OL,7,Falways more to do: "The running joke
OL,8,Fin the model railway community is that
OL,9,Fa railway is never finished.
OL,11,F"I do think I have run out of garden
OL,12,Fspace, so the track will probably have
OL,13,Fto stay as it is. But I think the
OL,14,Fthings that visitors will continue to
OL,15,Fsee evolve is probably more scenery,
OL,16,Fmore lights, more buildings.
