OL,3,CMeet the train fanatic using his
OL,4,Ctracks to help local causes
OL,6,F"There's also a few more interesting
OL,7,Ftechnical challenges that I want to
OL,8,Ftake on, which is computer control. So
OL,9,Fthe idea would be that eventually, you
OL,10,Fwon't need a manual operator, the
OL,11,Ftrains will just do it themselves."
OL,13,FCurtis and his girlfriend open their
OL,14,Fgarden to the public a few times a
OL,15,Fyear, but each time they raise money
OL,16,Ffor charities that are special to them.
