OL,3,CMeet the train fanatic using his
OL,4,Ctracks to help local causes
OL,6,FFunds from this weekend's event will
OL,7,Fbe going to Royals RFC and Jersey
OL,8,FRescue Dogs: "I love animals, I've got
OL,9,Fa dog myself and I think particularly
OL,10,Ffor Jersey Rescue Dogs, obviously they
OL,11,Fdo the rehoming and support with that,
OL,12,Fbut they also do all of the education
OL,13,Fthat comes around with having a rescue
OL,14,Fdog.
OL,16,F"I sometimes think humans don't
OL,17,Fdeserve dogs, they're just amazing
OL,18,Fcreatures. So to be able to support a
OL,19,Fcharity that does such amazing work
OL,20,Ffor them, I think is amazing."
